Maruchi Fresno https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maruchi_Fresno 0 Maruchi Fresno (February 14, 1916 – July 19, 2003) was a Spanish film actress. Fresno appeared in around sixty films and television series during her long career. In 1947 she played the role of Isabel of Aragon in the historical film The Holy Queen.
